name: Custom Signature Logos
description: Exclusive handwritten "signature" logos by Maria are the perfect way to brand your business and stand out among the competition. For a professional, polished appeal, logos have a "girly girl" feminine flair or a "brushed" artistic style for a unique identity brand. Browse the pre-designed Collection below, or order custom at the bottom of the page. Galleria di Luce prides itself in providing serious design, for serious business and specializes in your complete, coordinated identity. Custom orders include handwritten signature in both print and web-ready files. Each illustrated design is uniquely created from scratch, with a special focus on original, exclusive concepts. Please feel free to contact me prior to placing your order. I look forward to working with you! Not sure what you're looking for? View my extensive Collection of Pre-Designs HERE. Home »
